tem_assets/steam/apps/2430280/extras/f574a247e7e9bcce4e30f9c35a2eb041.avif?t=1770723370\" width=610 height=214 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the thrilling and mysterious story behind your internship manager Emily. Complete cases and find out the truth!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Do you have what it takes to master all cases and close them all for good?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>We only have one question left for you to answer:</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Who Did It?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 30 Detailed, Completely Unique Cases.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ID Card Collection & XP/Level System.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Available in English, French, German, Spanish, Italian & Dutch</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >High scores per case.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 4 Difficulty Modes, From Easy to Really Hard.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 Gamemodes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Clues, Hints and Suspect-info Per Case.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mysterious Storyline Connecting the cases together</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Soundtrack and Atmospheric Audio</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Game Statistics</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>... and much more to come!</i> </p>",
